{"msg":{"list":[{"title":null,"userName":"孙莹","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ajNVdqHZLLBxBvpnK6F4ictaCR7aW1oAKp2BkdbQk8tAqpPPkic3Pq15Tdz5Z2RpVtn713U8ad1wgoPTibmwM6Y4Q/0","content":"<img src=\"http://static.iqycamp.com/application-20170421220344-gkkcng7qo-.PNG\" style=\"max-width: 90%; -webkit-touch-callout: none; -webkit-user-select: none;\"><br>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":9025,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492783442000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"清若芷萱","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/PiajxSqBRaEIJNapj1ibLnckBHdMF2pbTnMtdF32UHoBS2qCrd6PeWxAUxf4yk54MhicSEib9dcvXWdFibbRh3ict7BQ/0","content":"价值观来说：可能与之起了冲突，或价值观有了改变<div>周边影响来说：比如销售员压力大，或是舆论导向，或是奖金配比不能满足，或是家庭父母亲人有了什么事情，或是身边人做别的行业比较成功同学聚会等等造成了压力心里不平衡等</div><div>情感态度来说：自己的动力改变，或是得到满足后有了新的目标</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":9005,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492778426000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"千幽","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98UNjBmKBWOicOVxDToZOY3YjGpQ0Lr8Wy7tKu4DFX9VWNBBD6vTeV18n7EqwV3cGJ5vWNj2QfwXTlN3tVBzmHnwl/0","content":"<ol><li>价值观：他认为销售明星没有销售总监title响亮，自己做这么久了都没升迁到销售总监，觉得自己的管理才能没有被公司看见并认可，很难受。</li><li>个性&amp;风格：他生性内向，跟人打交道需要耗费许多力气，虽然他总能说服顾客，但这种工作方式让他疲惫不堪。<br></li><li>周边影响：他找对象的时候发现，现在的姑娘不喜欢业务员，都喜欢程序员，再不济也得是个产品经理，他对自己的职业产生了深深地自卑。</li><li>情感与态度：好不容易小明找了个女朋友，却因为销售工作不定时，没能好好陪女友导致来之不易的爱情也要告吹了，他现在希望工作能够有更稳定的下班时间，可以让他处理生活中事情。<br></li></ol>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8982,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492774013000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Jill Ling","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4AyyZN53g2CvLEGicxZ4heLHooiaCVwibvbcw8BcDsxgL2AMj3bgU2wNX8OPexCoDeHxKxE9KicExhXd1G/0","content":"<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">1) 价值观</p><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">取决于销售的产品/公司文化是否符合他的价值观。比如如果公司销售的是烟草类产品，而小明本身是个非常注重健康的人，就会出现价值观不匹配的情况。或者公司本身文化非常激进，强调竞争，而小明是个注重合作的人，也会出现价值观的不匹配。</p><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">2）个性风格</p><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">销售需要经常跟不同的人打交道。如果小明本身的个性是个不喜欢交际的人，可能在开始的激情退却之后，会由于个性上的不匹配而产生厌倦</p><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">3）周边影响</p><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">如果家人对于销售工作的性质有意见，比如经常需要出差或者应酬，会影响小明的意愿。</p><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">或者周围同学大多去了收入/发展空间更大的互联网公司做产品等，也会影响小明继续工作的意愿</p><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">4）情感与态度</p><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">可能小明做这份工作的初衷是为了高奖金或其他目的，结果发现公司并没有兑现当初的承诺，会影响小明对这份工作的态度。</p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8818,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492737824000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"浅紫","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-20","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay5Qias5Y6BOJq0bibrmkolNJFtbyicK1y9rN41JY4SIw04awshr8lhByygakZc9SVzOfPej1XNTbShq/0","content":"待补充","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8712,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492703384000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":" 慧","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-20","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcLO4icY9WH8XVTJcKdfCeUuEbZWjdOKAJesWd1BIiaW3dVKFMYewT7WlLHEO0ODuJ6JcZ47UyLXibWoCIPG6JsCX9d/0","content":"1. 不认可产品的价值，推销过程违背自己的价值观<div>2. 性格内向，本质不喜与人打交道</div><div>3.觉得销售岗位社会地位低，工作忙无法兼顾感情家庭</div><div>4.更喜欢稳定、压力小的工作</div>","voteCount":1,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8699,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492701974000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"任鹏Rock","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-20","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6adoic3GoppNoNB1NxuxpynD2ib2aKxIUvPiczalMgvvOFtRYYxlB548Ha5woxAzeHON4RM4mSey7ibgoh4I3y9RicaD/0","content":"1价值观，销售中的灰色地带让看重诚实正直的小明很不舒服<div>2个性</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8627,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492693469000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"张金","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-20","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/wbKdib81ny69EdhI7icpfWiapKlOseWaauSC6a85Jkfhj1C5Q2grA62T4vG8aZFib7bKsNfXvWk0grabbFvibtzrwwg/0","content":"1、价值观方面：<div>（1）小明虽然擅长销售，但从来没有喜欢销售这个职业，不认可为了业绩而违背内心原则。</div><div><span style=\"font-size: 1.6em; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\">（2）因为工作性质，出差喝酒陪客户多、工作忙碌，小明内心更注重家庭和规律生活。</span></div><div>2、个性/风格方面：<span style=\"font-size: 1.6em; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\">小明本质是很内向的，长期的销售工作让他感到很疲惫，压力无法排解</span></div><div>3、周边影响：</div><div>（1）销售人员在众多人看来地位不高，小明长期受到舆论压力；</div><div>（2）由于工作太忙无法照顾家庭，小明的妻子对他的意见很大</div><div>（3）公司员工业绩压力大，同事间为了抢业务勾心斗角，小明开始厌恶这种工作环境。</div><div>4、情感与态度：<span style=\"font-size: 1.6em; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\">虽然业绩高，但是公司的奖金比例越来越低，小明动力减弱</span></div>","voteCount":1,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8625,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492693354000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"敏","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-20","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay36u84xJJa5xZVbSorVQsjiaRtdKff23d2pibDW0oSbVW3r0CUiaQtIg47Itf131L8acNXmLucqib4ibt/0","content":"<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">用知、愿、能来分析一下。</span></p><p><font color=\"#333333\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">知：是否清楚要做什么及相应要求</span></font></p><p><font color=\"#333333\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">愿：了解要做什么之后，有动力去做</span></font></p><p><font color=\"#333333\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">能：具备了意愿后，是否有足够能力来完成</span></font></p><p><font color=\"#333333\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">情境因素：是否有外部环境因素影响他人行为</span></font></p><p><font color=\"#333333\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\"><br></span></font></p><p><font color=\"#333333\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">从问题来看，小明的知、能都是满足的。那存在的问题，可能是愿和情境因素。</span></font></p><p><font color=\"#333333\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">一、愿</span></font></p><p><font color=\"#333333\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">（一）假设小明是个需要挑战的人：</span></font></p><p><font color=\"#333333\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">1.工作中没有新鲜感，</span></font><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">销售已经成为常规行为，没有过去刚开始接触做时的刺激。</span></p><p><font color=\"#333333\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">2.工作没有满足感。小明是个需要挑战的人，目前的销售工作他觉得太容易完成了，没有满足感。</span></font></p><p><font color=\"#333333\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">3.目前的工作职位让小明看不到发展的前途。</span></font></p><p><font color=\"#333333\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">4.虽然是销售明星，但收入并不高。不足以满足小明的需求。</span></font></p><p><font color=\"#333333\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">（二）假设小明是个希望安定的人：</span></font></p><p><font color=\"#333333\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">1.销售工作需要经常出差，小明不喜欢经常出差，居无定所。</span></font></p><p><font color=\"#333333\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">2.销售工作需要喝酒应酬，小明觉得厌倦了。</span></font></p><p><font color=\"#333333\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">3.销售需要和不同的人打交道，小明厌倦了。</span></font></p><p><font color=\"#333333\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">二、情境因素</span></font></p><p><font color=\"#333333\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">1.小明家里有事了，工作和家庭难以平衡。</span></font></p><p><font color=\"#333333\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">2.小明和女友分手了，情绪不佳。</span></font></p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8432,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492667849000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"stella\uD83D\uDD25","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-20","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XpSLeBeWNiaSicyupTSzFbVyoQhw811sPFadF2iaOsPXQ9eozl1e8WcgV3zu0YNXrAyFrOH2TCFPBF6WxhJV7Y21u/0","content":"<p>小明已经很擅长销售公司的产品，成功率很高，这样使小明现在工作没有难度，他很清楚知道这个顾客谈判到什么样就能成功，所以已经让他不用全身心投入销售这里了。当人们做事越来越熟悉越来越没有难度，能很轻松就做到或者做好，这个事情给人带来的满足感就会减低，这样就会给自己带来不好的感觉，越来越厌倦</p>","voteCount":1,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8385,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492660305000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"千利休","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-20","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJBkpIkVNa5FLhE0qcn4hibdztDwoFibnREIiamouUibBWIibIuvQwXtQldXFBkHiaZCym1ez0DoM1zRgTl8MvT5HmVFa/0","content":"周围影响：其他人认为销售这种职业很低贱。<div>个性：小明是个内向性格的人，尽管擅长与人沟通，但内心并不喜欢，讨厌无止无尽的聊天沟通。</div><div>价值观：小明认为销售出很多东西并不能创造价值，没有什么意义。</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8293,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492651705000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Frank","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-20","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/Q3auHgzwzM7VA9siaqMbYPxpsm8taM8kcrH5K4KhiaModo57T8R6B2J1L9t8cy6tF6Cibn8FvDwUVTxZ9x2gCibiazjecjG7DrtJ8hwfEGsCyUfY/0","content":"价值不认同，没有成就感，物质奖励不足","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8241,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492645970000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Ann熊婷","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-19","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6a1PuMwtm6NdEZnNAovgicl4iaXDdHjDlPo45oA5OrUhJmQZZo5ialVt3Pkt03M6BSbzVUGCH8IyWG1dicArYqtZJlk/0","content":"1.麻木 &nbsp;没有更好的激励反馈了<div>2.内心追求、人生理想没有想明白</div><div>3.有小术而无大道 &nbsp;多学学哲学，多尝试不同事情<br><div><br></div></div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8147,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492614105000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"费费费","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-19","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/PiajxSqBRaEKh1wxiazia9oicbpTScrS8vGw93gatumM8eVhK17IXibGHRWpo7L6L80ibpDKwuXcBotiaVxiczORtWjtTg/0","content":"1.成单率高，工资并没有较之前上涨，依然维持原状，可能到达了天花板<div>2.从事的工作可能比较枯燥，无法引起他的兴趣，不符合他的自我价值认同</div><div>3.可能受到了同事之间的排挤，人际关系不佳</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8094,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492611435000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"丁一鸣\uD83C\uDF3E","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-19","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/Q3auHgzwzM4vrefdoqnO2s5EthQOch2icOLgAMWGzN1u3RTa0jF61gc7DiabdIQ8NVMBJw520t41neAicNqEaMzCQ/0","content":"从知、能、愿三个角度分析，可以发现，能力层面小明没问题。因此，认知和意愿层面可能有些问题。<div><br></div><div>从认知角度：小明可能对于销售这个角色缺乏本质/长远角度的认知。</div><div>从意愿角度：也许小明对销售角色有足够的认知，但可能缺乏行为意愿，比如：</div><div>1）价值观不一致：比如他擅长销售，但他认为销售很功利；销售中的灰色地带触动价值观</div><div>2）个性/风格：比如他可能会觉得销售工作压力太大，他喜欢轻松一点的工作</div><div>3）周边影响：比如可能家庭发生变化，或者办公室氛围不好</div><div>4）情感与态度：比如不喜欢这家公司或领导</div>","voteCount":3,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7994,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492574493000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"张梦路","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-19","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6ZaLoY2RXU5FZibDrTsS1osmryDqKeuAvlF9licJ4nKDicnJ1HjwXTbvxdlVJj5oBJgqhR72iaGMxLcib1jJGsyWnUnj/0","content":"<p>原因：</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px;\">个人本身</span></p><p>是不是对新来的上级、同事不适应？</p><p>是不是对业务或企业文化不认同？价值观受到挑战？</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px;\">工作本身</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px;\">是不是没有得到适当 的正反馈和激励？</span></p><p>是不是最近工作压力大、重复度高，越来越对工作不满意导致的？</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px;\">其他因素</span></p><p>是不是最近家里出什么事了？或受社会、同辈的影响？</p><p>看了大家的答案，再修改：</p><p>随着健康状况下降、经济的富裕和销售工作（工资不满、升职无望、工作挑战减少）的瓶颈，他 的追求变了</p><p>同事离职增多（可能是<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px;\">竞争对手挖人、自己创业），</span>小明也对现在的工作开始怀疑、倦怠。</p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7990,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492570581000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Leo","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-18","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XpSLeBeWNiaSic0ds8BMCibGZ2OUAZx2wvLS7l0JfCujUnFH561QnYtbqvZs2sAcicsmYHVHeJSgYia20o2R8WfC0mn/0","content":"<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">1.个性/风格</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">原本个性就不适合，只是强迫自己适应；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">2.价值观</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">公司的发展与个人价值观发生冲突；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">更换了新的上司，小明不认可；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">3.周边影响</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">公司产品最近出现质疑的声音；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">家里人抱怨小明上班时间太长；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">原来的同事们纷纷离职；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">4.情感与态度</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">交了女朋友；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">追求的东西发生了变化；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">家庭里发生了较大的变故；</span></p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7966,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492511415000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"博学笃志","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-16","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/hglMZuicA3iauTIlciaKXMtjGcyXgjKvljRv5hsGdS0pUiaecGsLTmju6ib8JdHpQwqZqXeovGLB8HRWVxBjq0BaZpicsLFdj3dfibia/0","content":"<p>1、销售工作的价值观与其价值观不一致。</p><p>2、小明的个性、风格与销售工作的风格不匹配、</p><p>3、<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px;\">销售工作需要比较多的应酬，需喝酒，家人反对。</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px;\">4、<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px;\">销售工作竞争激烈，需要对金钱的渴望，小明对财富的渴望，并没有那么强烈。</span></span></p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7818,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492356255000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"放开那个小Joy","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-14","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XjoaHgicBwkEqUiaGZPHI2ga7E0gShutjcib8GKdDjQktSAdYIKa4icV4VOImzSz7BGe9nzia5iaxFMrTH0qEmSRDnhN/0","content":"工作带来的成就感削弱<div>没有相应的激励机制</div><div>个人职业发展意愿逐渐改变</div><div>周围同事或朋友的影响</div><div>业务中的某些操作违背自己的价值观</div><div><br></div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7689,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492136040000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"「Luffy」\uD83D\uDCB5","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-13","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6adoic3GoppNoO1fySK0bZ6tHCoze9icxn2FbpgeRT4GICDicGaOibHc99Z1z4QRVXfVWsAgVkX0abWl7EZs3ibtNSuV/0","content":"1.价值观<div>以前注重收入和成就。现在注重修养和多样化发展。<br><div>2.个性风格</div><div>以前好争，现在好守。</div><div>3.周边影响</div><div>以前有人追赶，现在高处很寂寞。</div><div>4.情感和态度</div></div><div>以前对销售明星很认可，很向往。</div><div>现在对销售明星习以为常，没什么大不了。</div><div><br></div><div>圈老，我觉得吧。分类不符MECE。1.3.4可归属同一类，即内因。内因再按1.3.4来分也有所重叠。价值观和态度其实都是对对象的评价和稳定性倾向，前者很大程度上影响了后者，即价值观认为当下阶段什么最重要，态度上就倾向它。个性虽然也会对态度有所影响，但可以分割。</div><div>我建议内因上分类：价值观，性格，情绪情感</div><div>归根究底，小明的内在原因是因为人的适应性作鬼，让他想有所变化。</div>","voteCount":1,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7612,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492013318000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]}],"highlightList":[],"end":false},"code":200}
